552
00:49:57,619 --> 00:49:59,204
Mama!

553
00:50:00,205 --> 00:50:01,456
Tae-seo!

554
00:50:03,917 --> 00:50:06,878
Dibandingkan dengan betapa Ibu sangat menyayangiku…

555
00:50:06,962 --> 00:50:08,046
